				\begin{document}$$ \mathrm{logit}\ \left(\mathrm{p}\right) = -2.522 + \left(1.268 \times \mathrm{DAD}\right) + \left(0.353 \times \mathrm{SOFA}\ \mathrm{score}\right). $$\end{document}logitp=−2.522+1.268×DAD+0.353×SOFAscore.
